# Android Studio / IntelliJ: local IDE + session state. These carry machine-specific
# paths (emulator AVD paths, usernames) and change constantly, so they don't belong in
# a public repo. Code style and inspection profiles are real project conventions and
# stay tracked.
.idea/*
!.idea/codeStyles/
!.idea/inspectionProfiles/

# Kotlin compiler session data
.kotlin/

# AI assistant working notes (plans, research) - local scratch, not project source
.artifacts/

# Build outputs, in case one is ever copied outside app/build/
*.apk
*.aab
